Class Auswerten

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.Netzwerk.de.Auswerten

  • public class Auswerten
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describe a interpreter of the XML file. The content of the XML file would be sort and store informations of the server in a TSInfo object.
